based only on the secret testimony
of the miserable souls...

9
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:09,516
who survived this
terrifying ordeal.

10
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:12,398
The incidents, places...

11
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:15,916
My friend, we cannot keep this
a secret any longer.

12
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,878
Can your heart stand
the shocking facts...

