31
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,511
What a show!
Everyone was terrifiic.

32
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:03,398
Paul, your second act monologue
actually gave me the chills.

33
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:06,392
- Oh, thanks, Eddie.
- I got the early edition,
hot off the presses!

34
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,311
This is the big moment.

35
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:21,158
- [Exhales]
- Oh, what does that old queen know?

36
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:23,071
She didn't even show.

37
